{
  "stem": "18575.6",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That's how tight we are forced to go in there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And started a two0weeks journey.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "No food, no water.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "First it was winter.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Those that were near the edge, which my friend that I was together, not friend-- we-- you tried to stick with somebody-- had a metal cup and a string.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "As the car moved, he could pick up some snow.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I mean, a spoonful.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Those inside that didn't have water or bread got crazy.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You don't die from hunger that fast, but you go crazy without water.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "You go crazy.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "You can't stand without water.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "With few days, and you're out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And they would die [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And they would freeze.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And we used to stack them up.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "In fact, sit on them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "We went to Poland, part because going forward Austria, we begged Polish railroad workers, and we Poles, we spoke Polish.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Please throw us snow.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And they would turn their back on us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "When we got to a-- near a town, and it's almost like an order, we should throw all the deaths out in front of the towns.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Just heave them out over the thing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "One day, the commandment of the transport, Mengele, you've heard of Dr.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Mengele?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He stopped the train with an automatic in his hand.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He says, I'll kill you all here if you do that one more time.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You're going to throw the dead when I tell you.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And from then on, he used to stop the train in open field and then tell us to dump it over-- over the-- So he was on the transport that you--",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was on the transport.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "On our transport going out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The-- we got-- they, they-- the train went through Poland to Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
